Package neqsim.pvtsimulation.regression

Class UncertaintyAnalysis

java.lang.Object
neqsim.pvtsimulation.regression.UncertaintyAnalysis
public class UncertaintyAnalysis extends Object
Uncertainty analysis results for PVT regression.

Provides parameter standard errors, confidence intervals, and correlation matrix from the regression optimization.

Version:
1.0
Author:
ESOL

    • UncertaintyAnalysis

      public UncertaintyAnalysis(double[] parameterValues, double[] standardErrors, double[][] correlationMatrix, double[] confidenceIntervals95, int degreesOfFreedom, double residualVariance)
      Create an uncertainty analysis result.
      Parameters:
      parameterValues - optimized parameter values
      standardErrors - standard errors for each parameter
      correlationMatrix - parameter correlation matrix
      confidenceIntervals95 - 95% confidence interval half-widths
      degreesOfFreedom - degrees of freedom (N - p)
      residualVariance - residual variance (chi-square / DOF)
